{
  "stem": "4570.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, but-- but it would be good if we have other relationships eventually.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because just the first love-- it's very dangerous to settle down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't like that at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was terribly possessive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and then we started talking about children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I actually never really wanted to have children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But because I was so much in love with him, I went with everything along.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so we talked how they will look.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I said, oh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I love if they look like you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he said, they should look like-- like you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so-- so we talked like probably all-- all teenagers talk when they're in love.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he was the first transport that went to Theresienstadt, which is Terezin, in Czech.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there-- there was a group of 1,000 young men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they went into that Theresienstadt, which is-- which is a garrison town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the army barracks, they had to prepare for the influx, which at that time, also we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they had to build for more and more people, obviously, those beds-- you know, the three-floor beds, and all that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the people were so rich, they could have bought the whole Jewish council.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why they didn't try to get those boys out of the transport-- and still they were ways to get them out of Czechoslovakia-- I never understood.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I even had this crazy idea to say maybe if Goldie would marry me, because I'm 1/2 Jewish, I-- I could protect him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nobody ever listened to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyhow--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, at that time we knew-- knew it-- it is starting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Something bad is starting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, there were always little bits and bits of something happening, like that the Jews have to hand over.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took all the properties away.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
